data.text: Kano is a Kameo Character in Mortal Kombat 1. He's appeared in other MK titles and is a native of Earthrealm who is often portrayed as one of the antagonists in the series. This Kameo guide will detail everything you'll need to know about using Kano, with information on how to complete combos, fatalities, and more.
